## PHP coding standard
  - name: "Follow Pint format standards"
    description: "Ensure code follows Laravel Pint standards"
    pattern: "function ([a-zA-Z_]+)\\("
    instructions: |
      - Follow PSR-12 coding standards
      - Indent with 4 spaces
      - Use snake_case for method names in tests
      - Use camelCase for method names in classes
      - Lines should not exceed 120 characters
      - Add trailing commas in multiline arrays
      - Order imports alphabetically
      - Follow pint.json rules defined in project